nt": "none"}, {"name": "facebook", "sentiment": "none"}]}, "highlightText": "", "language": "english", "persons": [], "text": "<img data-attachment-id=\"6367952\" data-permalink=\"http://metro.co.uk/?attachment_id=6367952\" data-orig-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/1959536_1457457061152196_1924870269_n-e1483866976449.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" data-orig-size=\"447,377\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"First British man to become pregnant\" data-image-description=\"<p>First British man to become pregnant</p> <p>REF:<br /> COLLECT VIA SOCIAL MEDIA<br /> https://www.facebook.com/pc.younger<br /> https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1457457061152196&set=ecnf.100006637476330&type=3&theater</p> <p>Picture: Facebook</p> \" data-medium-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/1959536_1457457061152196_1924870269_n-e1483866976449.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=300&strip=all\" data-large-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/1959536_1457457061152196_1924870269_n-e1483866976449.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=447&strip=all\" class=\"img-align-none wp-image-6367952\" src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/1959536_1457457061152196_1924870269_n-e1483866976449.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" alt=\"First British man to become pregnant REF: COLLECT VIA SOCIAL MEDIA https://www.facebook.com/pc.younger https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1457457061152196&set=ecnf.100006637476330&type=3&theater Picture: Facebook\" width=\"851\" height=\"718\" /></div><figcaption>Hayden Cross, 20, has become the first British man to announce he’s pregnant (Picture: Facebook)</figcaption></figure> <strong>A 20-year-old man has become the first in the Britain to announce that he’s pregnant.</strong>\nHayden Cross, who was born as a girl, has been living as a man for three years but put his transition on hold in order to have a baby.\n<a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/08/child-7-left-with-59-scars-following-savage-attack-by-american-bulldog-6367666\" data-track=\"zone-post-thumbnail-link\" data-track-destination=\"6367666\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230889450.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=100&h=75&crop=1\" data-aspect=\"1.3274336283186\" alt=\"LIVERPOOL, UNITED KINGDOM - OCTOBER 02: 02: An exterior view of Liverpool Crown Court, where the trial of Sean Mercer, age 18, accused of murdering schoolboy Rhys Jones begins today at Liverpool Crown Court on October 2, 2008 in Liverpool, England. Eleven-year-old Rhys Jones died in the car park of the Fir Tree public house, Croxteth, by one of three bullets that struck him in the neck, on August 22, 2007 whilst walking home after playing football with his friends. (Photo by Christopher Furlong/Getty Images)\" class=\"thumbnail-link-image\" data-rewritten=\"false\" /><span class=\"mor-title\">Child, 7, left with 59 scars following savage attack by American Bulldog</span></a> He is legally male and has begun hormone treatment but decided to have a child now rather than delay his transition..\nThe dad-to-be is now four months pregnant after finding a sperm donor on Facebook.\nHe had approached the NHS to see if his eggs could be frozen before completing his full gender change but was refused.\n<figure class=\"alignnone img-container shareable-item\" style=\"max-width:620px\"><div class=\"img-wrap\"><a id=\"item-attachment_6367948\" class=\"anchor\"></a><div class=\"item-share-buttons item-share\"><a class=\"share-item share-item-facebook btn\" title=\"Share this on Facebook\" data-track=\"share-item-facebook\"><span class=\"icon icon-facebook\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-twitter btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Twitter\" data-track=\"share-item-twitter\"><span class=\"icon icon-twitter\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-pinterest btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Pinterest\" data-track=\"share-item-pinterest\"><span class=\"icon icon-pinterest\"></span></a></div><img data-attachment-id=\"6367948\" data-permalink=\"http://metro.co.uk/?attachment_id=6367948\" data-orig-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230890876.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" data-orig-size=\"2500,1693\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"EVAN HURD PHOTOGRAPHY\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"A sperm bank is a facility or enterprise that collects and stores human sperm from sperm donors for use by women who need donor-provided sperm to achieve pregnancy. (Photo by Evan Hurd\\/Corbis via Getty Images)\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"First British man to become pregnant\" data-image-description=\"<p>A sperm bank is a facility or enterprise that collects and stores human sperm from sperm donors for use by women who need donor-provided sperm to achieve pregnancy. (Photo by Evan Hurd/Corbis via Getty Images)</p> \" data-medium-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230890876.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=300&strip=all\" data-large-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230890876.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=1024&strip=all\" class=\"img-align-none size-full wp-image-6367948\" src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230890876.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" alt=\"A sperm bank is a facility or enterprise that collects and stores human sperm from sperm donors for use by women who need donor-provided sperm to achieve pregnancy. (Photo by Evan Hurd/Corbis via Getty Images)\" width=\"1024\" height=\"693\" /></div><figcaption>Hayden became pregnant after finding a sperm donor on Facebook (Picture: Evan Hurd/Corbis via Getty Images)</figcaption></figure> <figure class=\"alignnone img-container shareable-item\" style=\"max-width:620px\"><div class=\"img-wrap\"><a id=\"item-attachment_6367957\" class=\"anchor\"></a><div class=\"item-share-buttons item-share\"><a class=\"share-item share-item-facebook btn\" title=\"Share this on Facebook\" data-track=\"share-item-facebook\"><span class=\"icon icon-facebook\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-twitter btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Twitter\" data-track=\"share-item-twitter\"><span class=\"icon icon-twitter\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-pinterest btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Pinterest\" data-track=\"share-item-pinterest\"><span class=\"icon icon-pinterest\"></span></a></div><img data-attachment-id=\"6367957\" data-permalink=\"http://metro.co.uk/?attachment_id=6367957\" data-orig-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230892577.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" data-orig-size=\"1713,2500\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"Kristian Dowling\\/TB\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Thomas Beatie and daughter Susan Juliette Beatie pose for a photo on March 16, 2009 in Bend, Oregon. (Photo by Kristian Dowling\\/Getty Images) BEND, OR - MARCH 16: (EDITORS NOTE: THIS IMAGE HAS BEEN DIGITALLY ALTERED) ***EXCLUSIVE ACCESS***\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"AD_230892577.jpg\" data-image-description=\"<p>Thomas Beatie and daughter Susan Juliette Beatie pose for a photo on March 16, 2009 in Bend, Oregon. (Photo by Kristian Dowling/Getty Images) BEND, OR – MARCH 16: (EDITORS NOTE: THIS IMAGE HAS BEEN DIGITALLY ALTERED) ***EXCLUSIVE ACCESS***</p> \" data-medium-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230892577.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=206&strip=all\" data-large-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230892577.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=702&strip=all\" class=\"img-align-none size-full wp-image-6367957\" src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/ad_230892577.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" alt=\"Thomas Beatie and daughter Susan Juliette Beatie pose for a photo on March 16, 2009 in Bend, Oregon. (Photo by Kristian Dowling/Getty Images) BEND, OR - MARCH 16: (EDITORS NOTE: THIS IMAGE HAS BEEN DIGITALLY ALTERED) ***EXCLUSIVE ACCESS***\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1494\" /></div><figcaption>Thomas Beatie and daughter Susan Juliette Beatie (Picture: Kristian Dowling/Getty Images)</figcaption></figure> Once he has given birth he will fully transition by having his breasts and ovaries removed.\nThe expectant father, who is from Gloucester, told <a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/2560070/british-man-20-will-be-the-first-to-give-birth-to-a-baby-thanks-to-sperm-donor-he-found-on-facebook/\">The Sun </a>on Sunday he is looking forward to becoming a father but is struggling with some of the physical changes.\n‘I was happy but I also knew it would be backtracking on my transition,’ he said.\n‘It is a very female thing to carry a baby and it goes against everything I feel in my body.\n‘I wanted the kid now so that I can have the transition before I get old.’\n<aside class=\"zone-post-strip\"><h3>More: <a href=\"https://metrouk2.wordpress.com/news/uk/\" data-track=\"zone-post-strip-more\">UK</a></h3><div class=\"zopo-item\"><a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/07/two-arrested-as-harrods-staff-protest-in-despute-over-who-keeps-their-tips-6367737\" class=\"zopo-link\" data-track=\"zone-post-strip-item\" data-track-destination=\"6367737\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhEAAJAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAE L QAAkAAAIKhI+py+0Po5yUFQA7\" data-src=\"http://i0.wp.com/metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/image-78.jpg?crop=54px%2C0px%2C480px%2C360px&resize=480%2C360&quality=80&strip=all&ssl=1&w=170&h=128\" data-aspect=\"1. \" data-rewritten=\"false\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /><span>Two arrested as Harrods staff protest in dispute over who keeps their tips</span>\n</a></div><div class=\"zopo-item\"><a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/07/missing-man-found-dead-in-canal-weeks-after-brutal-baseball-bat-attack-6367707\" class=\"zopo-link\" data-track=\"zone-post-strip-item\" data-track-destination=\"6367707\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhEAAJAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAE L QAAkAAAIKhI+py+0Po5yUFQA7\" data-src=\"http://i0.wp.com/metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/lee-liverpool-road.jpg?crop=180px%2C0px%2C842px%2C630px&resize=480%2C360&quality=80&strip=all&ssl=1&w=170&h=128\" data-aspect=\"1. \" data-rewritten=\"false\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /><span>Missing man found dead in canal weeks after 'brutal baseball bat attack'</span>\n</a></div><div class=\"zopo-item\"><a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/07/people-who-go-to-ae-with-toothaches-are-costing-nhs-up-to-18m-a-year-6367655\" class=\"zopo-link\" data-track=\"zone-post-strip-item\" data-track-destination=\"6367655\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhEAAJAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAE L QAAkAAAIKhI+py+0Po5yUFQA7\" data-src=\"http://i1.wp.com/metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/gettyimages-514771081.jpg?crop=68px%2C0px%2C1066px%2C799px&resize=480%2C360&quality=80&strip=all&ssl=1&w=170&h=128\" data-aspect=\"1. \" data-rewritten=\"false\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /><span>People who go to A&E with toothaches are 'costing NHS up to £18m a year'</span>\n</a></div></aside> In 2008, American Thomas Beatie became the first man in the world to announce that he was pregnant\nAnd Hayden said he plans on telling his child about his transition.\n‘I think I would tell it because it has the right to know,’ he continued.\n‘I’ll bring up the child in a trans environment so hopefully there won’t be any problem.\n‘Trans is a common thing now for our generation.’", "external_links": [], "published": "2017-01-08T16:27:00.000+02:00", "crawled": "2017-01-08T11:27:43.947+02:00", "highlightTitle": ""}